{"tid":881801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【特朗普鐵幕】高10米美墨圍牆 首階段落成","createTime":"2018-10-29T17:06:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T02:32:24.000Z","uid":57786,"like":31,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b63aba3822d755ed5cdeeca1e28dad97b485909d","tid":881801,"uid":57786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T17:06:36.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普堅持反移民的立場，第一階段的美墨圍牆亦已建好，以全面阻隔經墨西哥入境的非法移民。<br />\n<br />\n國土安全部長尼爾森（Kirstjen Nielsen）見證位於加州邊境城巿卡萊克西科（Calexico）的首階段圍牆落成，圍牆高30呎（約10米），她表示︰「所有事情已準備妥當。讓我清楚表明，圍牆已建立。」<br />\n<br />\n有工人將一塊寫有特朗普、尼爾森及數名高官名字的牌釘在圍牆上。尼爾森表示︰「我們在合法的基礎上尋找一切可行方法，確保那些沒有法律權利入境這國家的人不會入來。」<br />\n<br />\n是次所建的圍牆，與特朗普2016年競選時提出、於聖迭戈（San Diego）附近建築的圍牆原型分開。尼爾森在Twitter發言指︰「邊境安全就是國家安全。我們需要資金，繼續建造美國總統的圍牆。」<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》<br />\n<br />\n[url]<img src=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181029/58845685\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181029%2F58845685&h=6e301792&s={SIZE}\" />[/url]<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181028/large/1540716918_67a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181028%2Flarge%2F1540716918_67a4.jpg&h=56f976ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e96b6f65f5272caab72add2940baefcb444fb0a2","tid":881801,"uid":78143,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T17:07:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SVGZHDS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSVGZHDS.gif&h=c53909df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa40a583492556e94a8d3f64e5305452cf455dd7","tid":881801,"uid":57786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T17:07:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181029/58845685\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181029%2F58845685&d=gNd%2FZe%2F%2Ffi2rFZVpg4x76QRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=783f3d25\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181029%2F58845685&h=7074ef68\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181029/58845685</a>"},{"pid":"d824348e2283155f81bb6f6ceef36589b72c2aff","tid":881801,"uid":41524,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T00:37:21.000Z","msg":"墨狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返鄉下吸毒啦"},{"pid":"7992d4b24c709beb79b948011795a2c93bbfc41d","tid":881801,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T00:41:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有次睇discovery 美墨邊境 麻撚煩"},{"pid":"346a27e19eece00215733a1984d78376201658eb","tid":881801,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T00:42:56.000Z","msg":"其實佢諗住點樣叫墨西哥比錢"},{"pid":"401d7c9d78810bab5d24d59837216e9ff56d56ab","tid":881801,"uid":47674,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T00:45:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.abcnews.com/images/International/migrants1-rt-ml-180430_hpMain_4x3_992.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.abcnews.com%2Fimages%2FInternational%2Fmigrants1-rt-ml-180430_hpMain_4x3_992.jpg&h=b871f8ea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"78db1d794e2cf8375d13ad018d8a1402b0e81921","tid":881801,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T00:47:53.000Z","msg":"其實起左幾長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6632bdcbf1b3272f7de80f9f634c157cc1e522f","tid":881801,"uid":42982,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T00:54